What is AMPnet?
AMPnet is a whitelabel software platform aimed at real-estate companies,
renewable energy companies & private equity (VC) companies. AMPnet
enables companies to
● Finance your projects (raise from private investors or
crowdfunding/crowdlending campaigns) easier than ever before.
Handle hundreds of investors as easy as handling a single investor.
● Accept global investments -Accept investments from 170+
countries with processing fees as low as 0.49%
● Manage payments - When it’s time to pay profits to your investors,
our system saves you time & money by automatically handling
profit repayment
● Create a secondary market by allowing your investors to
automatically trade shares of their investments into your projects
● Automatic creation of tax reports & automatic portfolio tracking for
project owners and for investors.

Tokenize your projects - with one click
The tokenization of assets refers to the process of issuing a
digital token that represents a real tradable asset.
AMPnet allows our clients to effortlessly tokenize their financed
assets.
By enabling tokenization - your projects become much more
attractive to potential investors. These are just some of the
benefits that tokenized assets provide:
Trading & Liquidity. Tokenized assets can be freely traded OTC
or traded through exchanges (e.g. Uniswap)
Lending. Tokenized assets can be used as collateral on lending
protocols (e.g. SmartCredit)
Derivatives. Tokenized assets can easily be wrapped in
derivatives - giving them greater liquidity and stabilizing their
price. Wrap multiple assets into a single derivative and offer your
investors a much more liquid investment class.
Simulation: Using AMPnet Tokenized Real-Estate as
collateral for a DeFi loan
Legal structure tailored to your needs
If you’re just starting out in the fundraising business - we can
provide you with a set of templates to instantly kickstart your
fundraising journey. If you have your own legal structure -
AMPnet offers full flexibility to integrate your own model into
our platform.
Legal options available from AMPnet:
● Lien-On Model
Set a conditional lien on your real-estate or equity, use
it to securely finance & tokenize your assets. Ready in a
matter of days, fully compliant. Great for startups and
real-estate projects.
● Cooperative Crowdfunding
Use AMPnet for your existing cooperative or start a new
one. Great for community fundraising projects.
● Do it yourself
Our clients have full flexibility to set up their own legal
structure. Your project, your rules!
Retain full control
AMPnet gives you the all the tools you need to
finance your projects - while leaving 100% of the
control to you.
Your company
Usually, fundraising or tokenization platforms require
you to transfer your company shares to them or to
sign financing agreements under their terms.
With AMPnet, you make the rules and interact directly
with your investors - no intermediaries present.
Your account
With AMPnet - only you get access to the fundraising
accounts. No one else (not even AMPnet) can access
your funds.
All accounts come with escrow functionality - giving
your investors the security that funding will be done
according to predefined rules (set by you)
